article.headline: Glasper's 31 lead N.C. A&T past Texas Southern 85-79
article.description: — Landon Glasper scored 31 points as N.C. A&T beat Texas Southern 85-79 on Saturday night for its first win of the season.
article.linkText: Glasper's 31 lead N.C. A&T past Texas Southern 85-79
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Landon Glasper scored 31 points as N.C. A&T beat Texas Southern 85-79 on Saturday night for its first win of the season. Glasper also had seven assists and three steals for the Aggies (1-9). Camian Shell scored 13 points, going 4 of 8 from the floor, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and 4 for 6 from the line. Jalal McKie was 3-of-7 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range) to finish with 10 points. Grayson Carter led the way for the Tigers (0-8) with 19 points and four assists. Kolby Granger added 14 points and nine rebounds for Texas Southern. Jonathan Cisse also had 13 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
